=====================================
	*** Version 1.1.5 ***
—————————————————————————————————————

# Nowicka et al.'s F1000 CyTOF workflow integrated into CATALYST

o input 'flowSet', panel, and metadata are held in an
  object of the daFrame-class (inherits 'SummarizedExperiment')

o the constructor function daFrame() performs 'FlowSOM' clustering 
  and 'ConsensusClusterPlus' meta clustering

o newly available functions:

	- plotCounts 	      bar plot of event counts per sample
	- plotExprs 	      smoothed densities of marker expression
	- plotMDS 	      multi-dimensional scaling (MDS) plot
	- plotNRS 	      box plot of non-redundancy scores (NRS)
	- plotCodes 	      tSNE and PCA on 100 SOM codes
	- plotProportions     relative cluster abundances across samples
	- tSNE 	      	      runs tSNE on object of class daFrame
	- plotSNE 	      tSNE plot color coded by expression or cluster ID
	- plotExprHeatmap     median marker expressions across samples
	- plotClusterHeatmap  median marker expressions across clusters
	- mergeClusters       manual cluster merging

