=====================================
	*** Version 1.1.2 ***
—————————————————————————————————————

o estCutoffs():
  estimation of separation cutoffs using 4-parameter log-logistic regression

o computeSpillmat(), estTrim(): 
  options “method” and “interactions” allowing specification of
  how spillover should be estimated and which interactions to consider

o S. Chevrier and B. Bodenmiller added as authors

